How to decorate the perfect Christmas tree

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Creating the perfect Christmas tree is no easy task, but getting it right adds extra sparkle to the festive fun!

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
11 December 2013 Last updated at 06:22 GMT
So where do you start with the baubles and tinsel? How do you put the lights in the right place?  And should you make your own decorations?
Fear not, Nel and decorating expert Kat Croxford have got all the answers.
